fields.question: How do I book a cab using your app?
fields.answer: To book a cab, open the app, enter your pickup and destination locations, choose your preferred cab type, and confirm your booking. You'll then be matched with a driver.

fields.question: Can I schedule a cab in advance?
fields.answer: Yes, you can! Simply select the "Schedule Ride" option after entering your destination and choose your desired date and time for pickup.

fields.question: What if I need to change my destination during a ride?
fields.answer: You can change your destination mid-ride by updating it in the app. The fare will be recalculated based on the new route. Please inform your driver of the change as well.

fields.question: What payment methods do you accept?
fields.answer: We accept various payment methods including credit/debit cards, net banking, and popular digital wallets. You can add and manage your payment methods in the 'Payment' section of the app.

fields.question: How can I view my past ride receipts?
fields.answer: All your ride receipts are available in the 'Ride History' section of the app. You can view, download, or email them from there.

fields.question: How long does a refund take to process?
fields.answer: Once a refund is initiated, it typically takes 5-7 business days for the amount to reflect in your original payment method, depending on your bank's processing times.

fields.question: What should I do if my refund hasn't arrived?
fields.answer: If your refund hasn't arrived within the expected timeframe, please contact our customer support with your booking ID and refund reference number, and we'll investigate the issue.

fields.question: How do you ensure driver safety?
fields.answer: All our drivers undergo thorough background checks and vehicle inspections. We also have a continuous rating system to ensure high service quality and safety standards.
